    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>National Monument Designation Transparency and Accountability Act - Amends the Antiquities Act of 1906 to require land reserved as part of a national monument to be confined to the smallest area essential to ensure the proper care and management of the objects of historic or scientific interest protected by the monument. </p> <p>Sets forth additional procedures for the designation of national monuments under the Act.</p>]]></text>
